nglish (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>HTMLTableElement.createCaption()</strong></code>&nbsp;Methode gibt das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/caption\"><code>&lt;caption&gt;</code></a> Element zurück, das einer <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a> zugeordnet ist. Wenn in der Tabelle noch kein <code>&lt;caption&gt;</code> Element existiert, wird es durch diese Methode erzeugt&nbsp;und dann zurückgegeben..</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Anmerkung:</strong>&nbsp;Wenn noch keine Überschrift vorhanden ist, fügt <code>createCaption()</code>&nbsp;sie direkt in die Tabelle ein. Die Überschrift muss nicht eigens hinzugefügt werden, wie man es tun müsste, wenn man das&nbsp;<code>&lt;caption&gt;</code>&nbsp;Element mittels <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a> erzeugt hätte.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>HTMLTableCaptionElement</em> = <em>table</em>.createCaption();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Beispiel verwendet JavaScript, um eine Tabelle u